		<title>Weekend Read: Agreeing on green hydrogen</title>
		<link>https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/01/13/weekend-read-agreeing-on-green-hydrogen/</link>
					<comments>https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/01/13/weekend-read-agreeing-on-green-hydrogen/#respond</comments>
		
