		<title>World Bank moves forward with solar water scheme in Uganda</title>
		<link>https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/01/12/world-bank-moves-forward-with-solar-water-scheme-in-uganda/</link>
					<comments>https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/01/12/world-bank-moves-forward-with-solar-water-scheme-in-uganda/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Patrick Jowett]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 15:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
