		<item>
		<title>IEA warns of Australian rooftop PV slowdown amid high costs, grid issues</title>
		<link>https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/01/12/iea-warns-of-australian-rooftop-pv-slowdown-amid-high-costs-grid-bottlenecks/</link>
					<comments>https://www.pv-magazine.com/2024/01/12/iea-warns-of-australian-rooftop-pv-slowdown-amid-high-costs-grid-bottlenecks/#comments</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[David Carroll]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:15:56 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Commercial & Industrial PV]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Markets]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Residential PV]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[photovoltaic]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[photovoltaics]]></category>
